Class TaxCategoryQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.sphere.sdk.models.Base
      • io.sphere.sdk.queries.DefaultModelQuery<TaxCategory>
        • io.sphere.sdk.taxcategories.queries.TaxCategoryQuery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClientRequest<PagedQueryResult<TaxCategory>>, Requestable, EntityQuery<TaxCategory>, Query<TaxCategory>, QueryDsl<TaxCategory>

    public class TaxCategoryQuery
extends DefaultModelQuery<TaxCategory>
    Provides a QueryDsl for tax categories to formulate predicates, search expressions and reference expansion path expressions.

    For further information how to use the query API to consult the Query API documentation.
